= Kernel =

We seed only linux-image-*, as we don't need anything from restricted
for the virtual kernels.

 * Kernel-Stem: linux-image

== i386 ==

 * ${Kernel-Stem}-virtual [i386]

== Miscellaneous ==

 * grub [i386 amd64]
 * usplash
 * usplash-theme-ubuntu

== Filesystems ==

 * xfsprogs
 * jfsutils
 * lvm2
 * mdadm
 * dmsetup
 * cryptsetup

== For language support in the installer ==

 * console-terminus
 * unifont


